As Bobby, the man on top who
is constantly being pulled at from
all sides, Butler mesmerizes the
audience with quick, psychotic
energy. He hypnotizes with
brazen behaviorisms and lewd
analogies. Shanta brings excellent
comic timing to his lines as Fox,
the struggling producer. Wen
